[
    {
        "text": "To me, the most shocking thing about grit is how little we know,..",
        "startTime": 919,
        "endTime": 5303,
        "slowStartTime": 1529,
        "slowEndTime": 8179
    },
    {
        "text": "...how little science knows about building it.",
        "startTime": 5880,
        "endTime": 8103,
        "slowStartTime": 8970,
        "slowEndTime": 12379
    },
    {
        "text": "Every day, parents and teachers ask me,...",
        "startTime": 8768,
        "endTime": 10943,
        "slowStartTime": 13302,
        "slowEndTime": 16640
    },
    {
        "text": "...\"How do I build grit in kids?",
        "startTime": 11278,
        "endTime": 13007,
        "slowStartTime": 17067,
        "slowEndTime": 19736
    },
    {
        "text": "What do I do to teach kids a solid work ethic?",
        "startTime": 13304,
        "endTime": 16093,
        "slowStartTime": 20106,
        "slowEndTime": 24365
    },
    {
        "text": "How do I keep them motivated for the long run?\"",
        "startTime": 16491,
        "endTime": 18890,
        "slowStartTime": 24887,
        "slowEndTime": 28560
    },
    {
        "text": "The honest answer is I don't know.",
        "startTime": 19623,
        "endTime": 22368,
        "slowStartTime": 29585,
        "slowEndTime": 33777
    },
    {
        "text": "What I do know is that talent doesn't make you gritty.",
        "startTime": 24227,
        "endTime": 26747,
        "slowStartTime": 36491,
        "slowEndTime": 40346
    },
    {
        "text": "Our data show very clearly that there are many talented individuals...",
        "startTime": 27297,
        "endTime": 31767,
        "slowStartTime": 41095,
        "slowEndTime": 47876
    },
    {
        "text": "...who simply do not follow through on their commitments.",
        "startTime": 32040,
        "endTime": 34979,
        "slowStartTime": 48210,
        "slowEndTime": 52693
    },
    {
        "text": "In fact, in our data,...",
        "startTime": 35535,
        "endTime": 36782,
        "slowStartTime": 53452,
        "slowEndTime": 55398
    },
    {
        "text": "...grit is usually unrelated or even inversely related to measures of talent.",
        "startTime": 37061,
        "endTime": 42803,
        "slowStartTime": 55742,
        "slowEndTime": 64429
    },
    {
        "text": "So far, the best idea I've heard about building grit in kids...",
        "startTime": 44242,
        "endTime": 47841,
        "slowStartTime": 66513,
        "slowEndTime": 71987
    },
    {
        "text": "...is something called \"growth mindset.\"",
        "startTime": 48411,
        "endTime": 50439,
        "slowStartTime": 72766,
        "slowEndTime": 75883
    },
    {
        "text": "This is an idea developed at Stanford University by Carol Dweck,...",
        "startTime": 51149,
        "endTime": 54566,
        "slowStartTime": 76873,
        "slowEndTime": 82074
    },
    {
        "text": "...and it is the belief that the ability to learn is not fixed,...",
        "startTime": 54889,
        "endTime": 59689,
        "slowStartTime": 82483,
        "slowEndTime": 89758
    },
    {
        "text": "...that it can change with your effort.",
        "startTime": 60129,
        "endTime": 62311,
        "slowStartTime": 90344,
        "slowEndTime": 93691
    },
    {
        "text": "Dr. Dweck has shown that when kids read and learn about the brain...",
        "startTime": 63225,
        "endTime": 67271,
        "slowStartTime": 94987,
        "slowEndTime": 101131
    },
    {
        "text": "...and how it changes and grows in response to challenge,...",
        "startTime": 67573,
        "endTime": 70728,
        "slowStartTime": 101509,
        "slowEndTime": 106317
    },
    {
        "text": "...they're much more likely to persevere when they fail,...",
        "startTime": 71223,
        "endTime": 74838,
        "slowStartTime": 106985,
        "slowEndTime": 112482
    },
    {
        "text": "...because they don't believe that failure is a permanent condition.",
        "startTime": 75222,
        "endTime": 79699,
        "slowStartTime": 112983,
        "slowEndTime": 119773
    },
    {
        "text": "So growth mindset is a great idea for building grit.",
        "startTime": 80788,
        "endTime": 83893,
        "slowStartTime": 121332,
        "slowEndTime": 126064
    },
    {
        "text": "But we need more.",
        "startTime": 84413,
        "endTime": 85836,
        "slowStartTime": 126769,
        "slowEndTime": 128979
    },
    {
        "text": "And that's where I'm going to end my remarks because that's where we are.",
        "startTime": 86441,
        "endTime": 89554,
        "slowStartTime": 129812,
        "slowEndTime": 134556
    },
    {
        "text": "That's the work that stands before us.",
        "startTime": 89845,
        "endTime": 91965,
        "slowStartTime": 134918,
        "slowEndTime": 138172
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to take our best ideas, our strongest intuitions,...",
        "startTime": 92356,
        "endTime": 95917,
        "slowStartTime": 138684,
        "slowEndTime": 144101
    },
    {
        "text": "...and we need to test them.",
        "startTime": 96204,
        "endTime": 97733,
        "slowStartTime": 144456,
        "slowEndTime": 146825
    },
    {
        "text": "We need to measure whether we've been successful,...",
        "startTime": 98248,
        "endTime": 100596,
        "slowStartTime": 147522,
        "slowEndTime": 151119
    },
    {
        "text": "...and we have to be willing to fail, to be wrong,...",
        "startTime": 100960,
        "endTime": 104402,
        "slowStartTime": 151590,
        "slowEndTime": 156828
    },
    {
        "text": "...to start over again with lessons learned.",
        "startTime": 104792,
        "endTime": 107173,
        "slowStartTime": 157338,
        "slowEndTime": 160984
    },
    {
        "text": "In other words, we need to be gritty about getting our kids grittier.",
        "startTime": 108057,
        "endTime": 113464,
        "slowStartTime": 162236,
        "slowEndTime": 170421
    },
    {
        "text": "Thank you.",
        "startTime": 114085,
        "endTime": 114579,
        "slowStartTime": 171277,
        "slowEndTime": 172094
    }
]